➜去建国西路秘密洋房，赴一场新中式宴席！
http://www.sohu.com/a/429384595_380622	9750
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201104/98e1a538cbd74ede97a466e0ee724939.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>建国西路222号，</p>
<p>沪上食客熟悉的双层老洋房，</p>
<p>经过精心筹备与长达数月的细致打磨后，</p>
<p>终于在近期，</p>
<p>迎来90后名厨<strong>Chef Johnston</strong></p>
<p>与<strong>OPPOSITE集团</strong>的全新力作：</p>
<p><strong>Lunar！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201104/d1b8e32f97694cd5a75abc655536e548.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201104/55a2ad6095bc4adc9aeb39c12417af88.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
